{"id": 10, "name": "Texte de la commission sur la proposition de loi, apr\u00e8s engagement de la proc\u00e9dure acc\u00e9l\u00e9r\u00e9e, de M. Guillaume Kasbarian et plusieurs de ses coll\u00e8gues visant \u00e0 simplifier l'ouverture des d\u00e9bits de boisson en zone rurale (904 rectifi\u00e9)., n\u00b0\u00a01026-A0", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/1026/AN/10", "date": "2025-03-06", "status": "Adopt\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Yannick", "last_name": "Monnet", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Karine", "last_name": "Lebon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Soumya", "last_name": "Bourouaha", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9douard", "last_name": "B\u00e9nard", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Victor", "last_name": "Castor", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Andr\u00e9", "last_name": "Chassaigne", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Elsa", "last_name": "Faucillon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9meline", "last_name": "K/Bidi", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Paul", "last_name": "Lecoq", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Maillot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Maurel", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Marcellin", "last_name": "Nadeau", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Peu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Mereana", "last_name": "Reid Arbelot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Davy", "last_name": "Rimane", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Sansu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Tjibaou", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}], "summary": "Cet amendement vise \u00e0 donner un droit de veto aux maires des communes dont une licence de 4e cat\u00e9gorie est l'objet d'un transfert. Actuellement, le maire ne peut s'opposer \u00e0 un tel transfert que si la licence concern\u00e9e est la derni\u00e8re de sa commune. Permettre aux maires de s'opposer \u00e0 tout moment \u00e0 un tel transfert, et leur donner en cons\u00e9quence la possibilit\u00e9 de racheter les licences, permettrait aux collectivit\u00e9s de pr\u00e9server et de mieux ma\u00eetriser leur \u00e9conomie locale. Tel est le sens de cet amendement."}